title: Sengoku Hime Part 6
description: This is the latest game in Gesen18's Sengokuhime SLG series. Oda Nobunaga headed to the capital to fight against the Azai and Asakura clans. Houjou Ujiyasu planned to take down the led by the Yamanouchi Uesugi clan and claim all of Kantou. Takeda Shingen decided to exile his man Nobutora and take over control of the Takeda clan for himself. Masamune Date set forth to unite the Hokuriku region which had grown increasingly discordant. These are the warriors, along with the other clan heads, the wise strategist Amagi Souma, and the master swordsman Sakaki Tsukasa.
